          "nickname": "Supervision",
          "text": "On top of the grid, you have a target age. Your task is to find the face that matches the age."
        },{
          "nickname": "Supervision",
          "text": "You will start from the column on the left, and you can move to the next column if you find the correct face."
        },{
          "nickname": "Supervision",
          "text": "When you click on a face. It appears bigger on the right. It allows you to check if the face is the correct age. Click again on the small image to confirm your choice."
        },{
          "nickname": "Supervision",
          "text": "Be careful, images have been altered to try and trick face recognition!"
        },{
          "nickname": "Supervision",
          "text": "The game will start when you press the 'right arrow'. Be quick, be precise!"
        },{
